  "title": "Technician/Senior Technician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct engine disassembly from modular level to piece part level.</li><li>Ensure all maintenance activities are conducted in accordance with engine manuals, approved technical data and regulatory requirements.</li><li>Upkeep & maintain assigned equipment, tooling, and fixtures.</li><li>Adhere to all applicable EHS rules and regulations and report immediately any unsafe practices/conditions.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Nitec or Diploma in Aerospace, Mechanical Engineering or a related</li><li>Minimum 2 years’ work experience in disassembly/assembly/inspection in aviation industry</li><li>Good understanding of technical drawing and manuals.</li><li></li></ul><p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p><p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p><p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
